changes_made.rationale: Patient reported significant ongoing depressive symptoms (fatigue, anhedonia, early morning awakening, passive suicidal ideation) with minimal clinical improvement after 4 weeks on the 50mg dose, necessitating titration to the next therapeutic level.

get_chat_summary: **Change Proposed:** Dose increased from 50mg to 100mg daily to address ongoing moderate depressive symptoms.
**Peer Review:** **Match.** Current medication (*Sertraline*) aligns with the proposed diagnosis (**Recurrent Major Depressive Disorder, Moderate (F33.1)**).
